reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fun design with lots of levels!
reviews.reviewText: I like the design of this popit game with the fun astronaut helmet - it isn’t too babyish or weird but adds a little something extra. This version has over 200 levels which is insane! The buttons work as expected as do the lights and the sound can be modified based on how loud you want it. This is a great game for any age and is super portable. We like to leave these in the car for long car rides or throw into our carryon bag for plane rides. You do need to add batteries so just be aware of that. Would make a great stocking stuffer for any age!
